This package contains action classes responsible for mode-specific functionality.

Class Overview:

engine.mode.Mode        - Base abstract class for all modes.
engine.mode.BatchMode   - Implementation of the "batch" mode.
engine.mode.ConsoleMode - Implementation of the "console" mode.
engine.mode.ListMode    - Implementation of the server "list" mode.

######################################################################
